media:group.media:title: Every Current YouTube World Record
media:group.media:description:
When making a comparison of 2022 YouTube World Records, they range in difficulty from easy to impossible. There's anything from most disliked to most liked YouTube videos, most viewed videos to most liked comments, community posts and most voted polls. There's also a bunch of firsts - What was the first YouTube video? The first YouTube comment? The First video with a thumbnail? This video will cover every YouTube world record from easy to impossible.

This is, Every YouTube World Record - Easy to Impossible

Thank you guys for watching, like and sub if you enjoyed, SunnyV2 XO ‚ù§

Also, the idea for this video was inspired by "MrRanker" who posted a video on a similar topic in June 2021 titled "Comparison: YouTube World Records 2022" You can watch their version here - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0D9rxq90K4U&t=1s
